0_Aw_1976-09-18_Die_Welt_steht_Kopf_.jpg \"Award for 'Die Welt steht Kopf'\"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200110170136/http://www.roger-steinmann.com/images/710_Aw_1976-09-18_Die_Welt_steht_Kopf_.jpg |date=2020-01-10 }}. [http://www.roger-steinmann.com/awards.html ''ROGER STEINMANN -'' ''Awards''] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200110170136/http://www.roger-steinmann.com/awards.html |date=2020-01-10 }}. Retrieved January 12, 2020</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"row\" | 1977\n|Die Maschinentiere\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| Short Documentary; won Top-Award by Swiss Animal-Protection-Association\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |<ref name=\":9\">Max H\u00e4nsli (September 17, 1977) [http://www.roger-steinmann.com/images/710_D_1977-09-17_FLUTKATASTROPHE_MASCHINENTIERE,_Press_Release_Jugendfilmtage_with_Awards.JPG \"Press release about die 2. Schweizerischen Jugend Film Tage\"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200110170211/http://www.roger-steinmann.com/images/710_D_1977-09-17_FLUTKATASTROPHE_MASCHINENTIERE,_Press_Release_Jugendfilmtage_with_Awards.JPG |date=2020-01-10 }} incl. 'Die Flutkatastrophe' and 'Die Maschinentiere'. [http://www.roger-steinmann.com/filmdocuments.html ''ROGER STEINMANN - Film-Documents''] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200110170210/http://www.roger-steinmann.com/filmdocuments.html |date=2020-01-10 }}. Retrieved January 9, 2020</ref>\n|-\n|Die Flutkatastrophe\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n|Short film; won Award, aired in Swiss TV\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |<ref name=\":10\" /><ref name=\":13\" /><ref name=\":9\" /><ref name=\":11\">Schweizerische Jugendfilmtage (September 17, 1977). [http://www.roger-steinmann.com/images/710_Aw_1977-09-17_FLUTKATASTROPHE_,_Diploma_Schweizerische_Jugendfilmtage.JPG \"Award for 'Die Flutkatastrophe'\"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200110170136/http://www.roger-steinmann.com/images/710_Aw_1977-09-17_FLUTKATASTROPHE