ry of the Catholic Church}}\n{{Aristotelianism}}\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Aquinas, Thomas}}\n[[Category:Thomas Aquinas| ]]\n[[Category:1225 births]]\n[[Category:1274 deaths]]\n[[Category:13th-century Christian mystics]]\n[[Category:13th-century Christian saints]]\n[[Category:13th-century Italian writers]]\n[[Category:13th-century Latin writers]]\n[[Category:13th-century philosophers]]\n[[Category:13th-century Roman Catholic priests]]\n[[Category:13th-century Roman Catholic theologians]]\n[[Category:Angelic visionaries]]\n[[Category:Aristotelian philosophers]]\n[[Category:Burials at the Church of the Jacobins, Toulouse]]\n[[Category:Christian ethicists]]\n[[Category:Christian apologists]]\n[[Category:Christian anti-Gnosticism]]\n[[Category:Critics of atheism]]\n[[Category:Christian critics of Islam]]\n[[Category:Doctors of the Church]]\n[[Category:Dominican mystics]]\n[[Category:Dominican saints]]\n[[Category:Dominican theologians]]\n[[Category:Founders of philosophical traditions]]\n[[Category:International law scholars]]\n[[Category:Italian Dominicans]]\n[[Category:Italian nobility]]\n[[Category:Italian philosophers]]\n[[Category:Italian Roman Catholic priests]]\n[[Category:Italian Roman Catholic theologians]]\n[[Category:Italian Roman Catholic writers]]\n[[Category:Latin commentators on Aristotle]]\n[[Category:Magic (supernatural)]]\n[[Category:Medieval Italian saints]]\n[[Category:Medieval Latin poets]]\n[[Category:Metaphysicians]]\n[[Category:People from the Province of Frosinone]]\n[[Category:Roman Catholic moral theologians]]\n[[Category:Catholic philosophers]]\n[[Category:Scholastic philosophers]]\n[[Category:Supporters of witch hunting]]\n[[Category:Systematic theologians]]\n[[Category:Thomist philosophers]]\n[[Category:Virtue ethicists]]\n[[Category:University of Naples Federico II alumni]]\n[[Category:University of Paris alumni]]\n[[Category:13th-century jurists]]\n[[Category:Philosophers of law]]\n[[Category:Writers about religion and sci